Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.abstract: Your Request POST call to the /payments endpoint is received and registered and the Ecospend Gateway is currently interacting with the bank’s system to respond you with a Response.

Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.name: awaitingAuthorization

Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.name: authorised
Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.abstract: The PSU has authorized the payment from their banking system. This is a very brief interim state that will NOT trigger webhooks.

Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.name: verified
Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.abstract: The ASPSP has authorized and accepted the payment for processing. The payment is not completed yet, it has not been sent through the corresponding payment rails. The payment can still be rejected by the ASPSP.

Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.name: completed
Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.abstract: The Payment is considered as completed when the payer’s ASPSP has sent the payment through the corresponding payment rails to be credited to the payee account.

Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.name: canceled
Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.abstract: The PSU has cancelled the payment flow.

Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.name: failed
Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.abstract: Payment flow has failed due to an error.

Enums/PaymentStatus.html#/s:9PayByBank13.name: abandoned
